Class HeaderFooterRecord

    public final class HeaderFooterRecord
extends StandardRecord
    The HEADERFOOTER record stores information added in Office Excel 2007 for headers/footers.(HEADERFOOTER记录存储Office Excel 2007中添加的标题/页脚信息。)

      • getGuid

        public byte[] getGuid()
        If this header belongs to a specific sheet view , the sheet view?s GUID will be saved here.

        If it is zero, it means the current sheet. Otherwise, this field MUST match the guid field of the preceding UserSViewBegin record.

        (如果此标题属于特定的图纸视图，那么图纸视图？的收件箱将被保存在这里。如果为零，则表示当前工作表。否则，此字段必须与前面的userSiewBegin记录的guid字段匹配。)
        Returns:
        the sheet view?s GUID(表格视图？s)
